data.description: OPPORTUNITY AWAITS! MOVE IN EQUITY in this gorgeous, beautifully maintained 2-story, located in Fox Grove! This better than new cream puff offers an inviting spacious floor plan with a spacious kitchen, quartz countertops, white subway tile, ample white cabinetry and generous island. SS appliances, gas range, wide plank laminate flooring throughout the main level, upstairs features spacious primary suite with luxury 5-piece bath and his and hers closet, 3 additional bedrooms with wall in closets, convenient upstairs laundry, full unfinished basement for future expansion, extended patio for entertaining! This is a MUST SEE for any discriminating buyer!
